Apple today <a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MGYX4LL/A/magic-keyboard-for-ipad-air-11-inch-m3-us-english">released</a> a new version of the Magic Keyboard for <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/ipad-air/">iPad Air</a> in black.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/10/magic-keyboard-for-iPad-air-11-inch-16x9-feature.jpg" alt="" width="1120" height="630" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1023267" /><br/>
Previously, the Magic Keyboard for &zwnj;iPad Air&zwnj; was only available in white. It is based on the older Magic Keyboard for the <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/ipad-pro/">iPad Pro</a> and &zwnj;iPad Air&zwnj;, which was available in both black and white, and was replaced by a redesigned version with a aluminum top case, backlighting, and a trackpad with haptic feedback last year. <br/>
<br/>
